- `apps/dashboard/src/app/api/projects/[id]/deployments/[deploymentId]/logs/route.ts` returns completed build logs from S3.
- The dashboard deployment detail page can display colored build output for completed builds.
- The CLI can fetch log text for the `gblockparty logs` command.
